    <wpt lat="50.1558917" lon="-5.1642958">
        <name>"No Bull" diversion</name>
        <desc>GPX route diverts right here to follow road route northwards to Stithians. Straight on will give some excellent bridleway but with several gates and some people have found the large beef cattle here a bit intimidating </desc>
    </wpt>
    <wpt lat="50.1641230" lon="-5.1593430">
        <name>Caution</name>
